name: Shape_estimateNTest
description: Unit tests for the estimateN method of the Shape class in Apache Commons Collections4 Bloom Filter.

test_cases.name: testEstimateN_ZeroCardinality
test_cases.description: Tests the estimateN method with zero cardinality.

test_cases.name: testEstimateN_HalfCardinality
test_cases.description: Tests the estimateN method with half of the maximum cardinality.

test_cases.name: testEstimateN_FullCardinality
test_cases.description: Tests the estimateN method with full cardinality.

test_cases.name: testEstimateN_ExceedsCardinality
test_cases.description: Tests the estimateN method with cardinality exceeding the maximum.

test_cases.name: testEstimateN_DifferentShape
test_cases.description: Tests the estimateN method with a different shape configuration.
